        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 24 at 3:26PM MDT until August 24 at 4:00PM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>SVRPUB

The National Weather Service in Pueblo has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
South central El Paso County in east central Colorado...
North central Pueblo County in southeastern Colorado...

* Until 400 PM MDT.

* At 326 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Pinon, or 16
miles north of Pueblo Airport, moving southeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect
wind damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

* Locations impacted include...
Pinon and Pueblo West.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
